### **Game Summary**

The main character is a lonely skunk. Their goal is to ultimately spray every human he sees in hopes of becoming their friend. The skunk faces obstacles of scaring away the bystanders because of their unpleasant smell. The setting takes place in the big city of Stinksborough. The skunk is the protagonist. The skunk spray is a game mechanic we used to make our game unique.

### **Character**

Our main character is a small skunk with an adventurous and playful personality, but he sometimes feels lonely. For this reason, his goal is to walk around the city and spray his scent on every human he sees, so everyone will be like him, and he can have more friends.

### **The World**

The world is a big city named **Stinksborough**. It is supposed to reflect a simulation of an actual city.

It’s a small city with a lot of activity. It has tall buildings and parks where our main character can move freely wherever he wants. We set the city in a modern time period, between the years 2020-2024, located in southern Canada. It has a warm climate and various types of NPC characters you can encounter due to the city’s cultural diversity. It’s a lively and cheerful city, with a typical day resembling what we see in our everyday lives, (including the constant scent of skunks in the air).

### **Key Concepts**

The main idea behind the game mechanics was to create a game that allows you to have a good time without any pressure, something more relaxed that you can play to take a break or enjoy yourself for a while. The mechanic we used is “Spray,” a little skunk who wants to spray his scent on every human around him. We added limits to the spray to make it more dynamic and included a counter to keep track of how many humans you’ve sprayed.![][image4]
